name: Wedding Pearl
description:
This paduka-inspired sandal has beautiful pearl detail. "Brides-to-be!", these are perfect for an outdoor summer wedding! Or as a second pair of shoes for when you want to retire those uncomfy bridal high heels!
(Or pair simply with flowy, summer dresses, or jeans and t-shirt to add some uniqueness to your outfit.)

One-of-a-kind! Only 15 pairs of these were made, so you are virtually guaranteed an original- unless you recommended them to another biride-to-be!- and in that case, you WERE there first! :)

Available in size 6,7,8,9.

Please note: This is a 100% handmade shoe. The insole is made of leather for quality and comfort. The outsole is made of recycled rubber for traction, cushion and comfort. All original hand made feesk sandals have the FK logo on the insole. The shoe size can be found in the big toe area.
